  POP_ASSUM MP_TAC >>
  FULL_SIMP_TAC list_ss [listTheory.MEM_FILTER] >>
  SIMP_TAC (list_ss++boolSimps.CONJ_ss) [listTheory.MEM_EL, rich_listTheory.EL_DROP] >>
